  "title": "Desecrated Deck",
  "description": "Desecrated Deck is a dark card game set in a cursed cellar where every move teeters between life and death. Use mystical perks and fate-driven cards to strike deadly pacts, defeat your opponent, and survive the malevolent forces – or be claimed by darkness.",
  "longDescription": "<!--image-->\n![Desecrated Deck-24n4d](https://cdn1.epicgames.com/spt-assets/ff1cea0bd57d4fce904bdc9d0723faa6/desecrated-deck-24n4d.jpg)\n\n<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# Desecrated Deck\n<!--text-->\nEnter the haunted world of Desecrated Deck, a dark card game set in a cursed cellar where every decision brings you closer to survival or your doom. Use Item Cards and eerie Perk Cards, each with unique powers, to manipulate fate, defeat your opponent, and navigate the malevolent forces that lurk within.\n\nGameplay Mechanic\nDesecrated Deck combines strategy and chance with the classic rock-paper-scissors mechanic. After each round, the winner chooses from a set of powerful Item Cards, each with unique effects that can dramatically shift the game. Every decision matters for survival. Use your wit to outsmart your opponent and shape the fate of the game in your favor.\n\nItem-Cards\nWith 6 unique Item Cards, players face risks and rewards. The Revolver for example can end an opponent’s life with a single shot, while the Pest Doctor restores one life to its user, changing the course of the game.\n\n<!--image-->\n![Desecrated Deck-1osz9](https://cdn1.epicgames.com/spt-assets/ff1cea0bd57d4fce904bdc9d0723faa6/desecrated-deck-1osz9.jpg)\n\n<!--textBlock-->\n<!--text-->\nPerk-Cards\nPerk-Cards allow you to defend yourself or sabotage your opponent. Use them strategically to manipulate Item Cards or weaken your enemy’s chances of success. From The Poisoned Mushroom to The Cursed Mirror, these cards offer dark powers that can turn the tide in your favor.\n\n<!--image-->\n![Desecrated Deck-1oiqi](https://cdn1.epicgames.com/spt-assets/ff1cea0bd57d4fce904bdc9d0723faa6/desecrated-deck-1oiqi.jpg)\n\n<!--textBlock-->\n<!--text-->\nAtmosphere and Visuals\nWith chilling visuals, eerie soundscapes, and immersive audio, Desecrated Deck immerses you in a haunted experience.\n\nWill you survive the Desecrated Deck, or will the darkness consume you?\n",
